│   %ext = zext i16 %add to i32                                                                                                                                                            │
│   %indvar.next = add i16 %indvar, 1                                                                                                                                                      │
│   br i1 false, label %for.body, label %for.end                                                                                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ for.end:                                                                                                                                                                                 │
│   ret i32 %ext                                                                                                                                                                           │
│ }                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ The loop is infinite due to `br i1 false`. The `for.end` block is unreachable.                                                                                                           │
│ The `indvars` pass is trying to find a closed-form expression for `%ext` on the loop exit.                                                                                               │
│ `%indvar` is an induction variable: `Start = -12`, `Step = 1`.                                                                                                                           │
│ `%ext` is derived from `%indvar`: `%ext = zext i16 (2 * %indvar) to i32`.                                                                                                                │
