│ `%indvar` (first iter) = -12 (0xfff4).                                                                                                                                                   │
│ `%add` = -12 + -12 = -24 (0xffe8).                                                                                                                                                       │
│ `%ext` = `zext i16 0xffe8 to i32` = 65512 (0x0000ffe8).                                                                                                                                  │
│ The target code has `ret i32 131048` (0x0001ffe8). The difference is one bit, `0x10000`.                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ This suggests an issue with sign/zero extension when computing the exit value of a SCEV expression. The expression for `%ext` is `{zext(2 * %indvar)}`.                                  │
│ The `indvars` pass uses `SCEVExpander` to generate code for the exit value.                                                                                                              │
│ The problem likely lies in `InductionDescriptor::transform`, which handles creating the exit value.                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ Looking at the `InductionDescriptor::transform` function in `llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/IndVarSimplify.cpp`, there's a part that handles creating the exit value. It computes the exit   │
│ count and then the value of the induction variable at that count.                                                                                                                        │
