│ The SCEV for `%add` is `{-24,+,2}<%for.body>`.                                                                                                                                           │
│ The SCEV for `%ext` is `(zext i16 {-24,+,2}<%for.body> to i32)`.                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The `SCEVExpander` has a `visitZeroExtend` method. This is where the code for the `zext` is generated.                                                                                   │
