│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The `visitZeroExtend` in `SCEVExpander.cpp` looks like this:                                                                                                                             │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ Value *SCEVExpander::visitZeroExtend(const SCEVZeroExtendExpr *S) {                                                                                                                      │
│   // ...                                                                                                                                                                                 │
│   Value *V = expand(S->getOperand());                                                                                                                                                    │
│   // ...                                                                                                                                                                                 │
│   return Builder.CreateZExt(V, S->getType(), V->getName() + ".zext");                                                                                                                    │
